heDropoutclassintheDropoutLayerofthemlp.layersmodule. Youneedtoimplement fpropandbpropmethodsforthisclass.'}, {'id': 'b11d0fc1-d08b-4343-b4be-21607a535c91', 'task': 'Implement L1Penalty and L2Penalty classes in mlp.penalties with __call__ and grad methods and integrate via weights_penalty and biases_penalty in AffineLayer', 'duration': 2, 'source_sentence': 'ImplementtheL1PenaltyandL2PenaltyclassintheL1PenaltyandL2Penaltyofthemlp.penaltiesmodule. Youneedtoimplement__call__andgradmethodsforthisclass.'}, {'id': '64c31edd-d8fd-469a-bd9b-acf9067bd722', 'task': 'Implement the combined L1 and L2 weight penalty as L1L2MixPenalty in mlp.penalties', 'duration': 1.5, 'source_sentence': 'Implement your proposed L1 and L2 combined weight penalty, as the L1L2MixPenalty in the mlp.penaltiesmodule.'}, {'id': '37010c13-4440-4d69-b22d-01a183cf9291', 'task': 'Run the supplied unit tests (DropoutandPenalty_tests.ipynb) to verify implementations of Dropout, L1Penalty and L2Penalty', 'duration': 1, 'source_sentence': 'Verifythecorrectnessofyourimplementationusingthesuppliedunittestsin DropoutandPenalty_tests.ipynb'}, {'id': 'efeed142-0d77-49ea-a44b-35f0aca47e0f', 'task': 'Run scripts/generate_regularization_layer_test_outputs.py with your student ID to generate xxxxxx_regularization_test_pack.npy', 'duration': 1, 'source_sentence': 'Todothispartsimplygotothescriptsfolderscripts/andthenrun python generate_regularization_layer_test_outputs.py --student_id Sxxxxxx replac- ingthe‘studentid’withyourstudentnumber.'}, {'id': 'cbb7bdbe-d0b5-4b71-832a-7ec10e895a8f', 'task': 'Train 1-hidden-layer networks with 32, 64 and 128 ReLU hidden units (1-hidden-layer = two layers total) on EMNIST using Adam and provided hyperparameters for 100 epochs; visualise and discuss effects on validation performance', 'duration': 2, 'source_sentence': 'Varyingnumberofhiddenunits. Initiallyyouwilltrainvarious1-hiddenlayernetworksbyusingeither32,64 and128ReLUhiddenunitsperlayeronEMNIST.'}, {'id': 'd18898fa-b1e8-4c4c-a6bc-7f172ad8f8f5', 'task': 'Train networks with 1, 2, and 3 hidden layers (128 ReLU units per layer) on EMNIST using Adam and provided hyperparameters for 100 epochs; visualise and discuss effects on validation performance', 'duration': 2, 'source_sentence': 'Varyingnumberoflayers. Hereyouwilltrainvariousneuralnetworksbyusingeither1,2,3hiddenlayerswith 128ReLUhiddenunitsperlayeronEMNIST.'}, {'id': 'a926d22a-f659-499f-8c80-265c6d612401', 'task': 'Modify the baseline network to use DropoutLayer, L1Penalty, or L2Penalty (and run a labelsmoothing-only experiment) using a baseline of 3 hidden layers, 128 units, ReLU, and Adam (lr=1e-4); train each model and record results', 'duration': 2, 'source_sentence': 'For the experiments,your baseline network should contain 3 hidden layers and 128 hidden units with ReLU activation function.'}, {'id': '50f3d5ee-3c1a-4e54-9eab-33770d0462da', 'task': 'Identify and run a set of 4 different hyperparameter combinations for your combined L1 and L2 experiments and record/argue selection', 'duration': 2, 'source_sentence': 'You willhavetoidentifyandargueforasetof4differenthyperparametercombinationsforwhichyouwillrun thecombinedL1andL2experiments(foryourimplementation).'}, {'id': '99f5d007-369f-4ba1-9226-89e09c7b6782', 'task': 'Run the labelsmoothing experiment without other regularisation techniques and record its effects', 'duration': 1.5, 'source_sentence': 'You shouldrunthelabelsmoothingexperimentwithoutotherregularizationtechniques.'}, {'id': '08008ec3-0315-4a76-9702-2be9c18ea56c', 'task': 'Investigate and explain performance problems of the provided model setup that uses the CustomActivationLayer', 'duration': 2, 'source_sentence': 'Youwillfinallyinvestigateandexplaintheperformanceproblemswithaprovidedmodelsetupandexperiment run,thatusesacustomactivationlayer.'}, {'id': '8ff4df1d-779b-4f63-9284-feafead04e2c', 'task': 'Populate mlp-cw1-questions.tex with your student number (replace SXXXXXX) and answer the template questions, include 